<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>It’s my pleasure to announce that <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-restdocs">Spring REST Docs</a> 1.1.1.RELEASE is available from Maven Central, JCenter, and our <a href="https://repo.spring.io/release">release repository</a>. My thanks to everyone who contributed to this release by reporting bugs and opening pull requests.</p>
<p>This maintenance release includes a <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-restdocs/issues?q=milestone%3A1.1.1.RELEASE">number of bug fixes</a> and is a recommend upgrade for all Spring REST Docs users. </p>
